Script info:
  description: Deletes a connection
  input:
    target:
      description: Target service
      default: Digital.ai Platform

---
Get accounts: ${input.target}
As: ${accounts}

---
Prompt:
  description: Select account to delete
  choices: ${accounts}
  type: select one
  display: name
As: ${account}

Delete account:
  target: ${input.target}
  name: ${account.name}

Print: Deleted ${account.name} in ${input.target}